high_descs: Go forward to the white table in the left corner.
Pick up the apple on the corner of the table.
Go to the front of the microwave on the top of the table.
Place the apple inside the microwave.
Turn left and go to the trash can on the floor on the left of the table with the microwave.
Take out the apple in the trash can
Go to the front of the microwave again.
Place the apple in the microwave on the left of the first apple.
Turn around and go to the right side of the white table on the left.
Pick up the gray knife on the table.
Go around the white table back to the front of the microwave.
Cut both apples inside the microwave into three parts.
anns.task_desc: Put two apples in the microwave and cut them.

high_descs: Go to the trash can next to the microwave stand.
Pick up the apple on the stand.
Move to face the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
Move left around the stand to the trash can.
Pick up the apple in the trash.
Move back to face the front of the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
Go to the table with one wooden chair.
Pick up the butter knife on the table.
Take the butter knife to the microwave.
Slice the apple on the right in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put an apple and apple slices on the plate in the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the microwave stand ahead of you, to the left.
Pick up the apple on the on the front, right corner of the microwave stand.
Walk to the front of the microwave ahead of you.
Place the apple inside the microwave.
Go to the left side of the garbage can on the floor to the left of the microwave stand.
Pull the apple out of the garbage can.
Go back to the front of the microwave ahead of you.
Place the apple in the microwave.
Turn around and go to the end of the white table, then turn to you are facing the microwave.
Pick up the knife in the center of the table.
Turn to your left and walk around the table, back to the microwave, across from you.
Cut both apples in the microwave into slices.
anns.task_desc: Cut two apples in the microwave into slices.
